main event: Two Louisiana state troopers photographed three globe-shaped UFOs at treetop level near the England Air Force Base in Louisiana on June 23.
interesting points: The troopers described the objects as spherical in shape and displaying flashing lights.
The troopers stopped to observe the objects, which hovered for several minutes before accelerating and disappearing.
The troopers took several photographs of the objects, showing their spherical shape and flashing lights.
The incident was investigated, but no further information was obtained about the identity or origin of the UFOs.
The existence of these authentic UFO photographs was officially confirmed by authorities of England's Air Ministry, but they were considered 'Top Secret' due to the close-up nature of the images.
location: Near England Air Force Base, Louisiana
